TITLE=New Features & Bug Fixes
DATA=2026-07-17
- Added Weather SPEED slider under Weather dropdown (range 0-5) to control particle rate, speed and lifetime
- Added Match Log entry for local player kills: shows "LocalName Killed VictimName with WeaponName" (local name in purple)
- Added Kill Effect trigger when the killer ID matches the local player ID
- Added real spectator resolution using LocalPlayer Spectators attribute
- Added custom cursor rendering when any Eclipse GUI is open (detects protected UI via gethui)
- Exposed _G.EclipseAS_SendKill so other modules can reuse the AutoSkill shoot packet path
- Silent Aim now targets the closest head in full 360 range using 3D Euclidean distance

TITLE=Bug Fixes & Performance
DATA=2026-07-17
- Fixed massive lag when holding a knife with AutoSkill or TriggerBot enabled (increased melee back-off interval to 0.6s)
- Fixed Glass Effect being applied to dead players; it now only applies to alive players and is removed on death, reapplied on respawn
- Fixed spectator list not updating when a player left the server
- Fixed custom cursor not appearing when opening the GUI
- Fixed Wallbang not firing on MB1 hold (feature later removed per request)
- Fixed spectator panel showing per-line numbered rows; reverted to simple "SPECTATORS: N" header count
- Removed Wallbang feature entirely to reduce overhead
